= render 'navbar'
- avatar_size = 34
- avatar_path = "holder.js/#{avatar_size}x#{avatar_size}"
.card-page

  .card-row
    .card
      .card__content
        %h1.card__title Where should we go on our Loomio retreat in October?

  .card-row
    .card
      .card__content
        .avatar-list
          .avatar-list__item
            %img{src: avatar_path}
          .avatar-list__item
            %img{src: avatar_path}
          .avatar-list__item
            %img{src: avatar_path}
          .avatar-list__btn.btn.btn-primary Invite

  .card-row
    .card
      .card__content
        .media-header
          .media-header__img
            %img.media-object{alt: "...", src: avatar_path}
          .media-header__text
            %h4.media-header__title Discussion notes
            .media-header__details Edited 30 minutes ago
        .media-content
          Several considerations should be taken into account when we choose where we'd like to stay...
           
          1. Cost should be less than $200pp
          2. Should be warm!
          3. Must have internet access. :)

  .card-row
    .card
      .card__content
        .media-header
          .media-header__img
            %img.media-object{alt: "...", src: avatar_path}
          .media-header__text
            %h4.media-header__title Vivien Maidaborn
            .media-header__details 2 hours ago
        .media-content
          So we need to decide a place to stay for our retreat. How about Riverslea? It seems like the right size, it's a great vibe, and the food was good too.
      .toolbar-container
        .toolbar
          .toolbar__button.toolbar__button--first
            %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-thumbs-up
            Like
          .toolbar__button
            %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-comment
            Reply
